title: CLP defector Larisa Lee happy to work with Adam Giles NT Government, despite bitter history
text: Independent MLA Larisa Lee says it is not worth staying angry with the party from which she defected amid mud-slinging on all sides - and says she will work with the Country Liberals Government to effect changes in the bush. ...
